{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, policy silos exist within and across countries and institutions in the public and private sectors.",
    "These silos make it difficult to aggregate data and derive meaningful insights even within one country 109.",
    "Policy silos also impact which data are prioritized for collection and which are overlooked 110, and contribute to issues related to data privacy and sharing.",
    "Different institutions have varying policies around data privacy and sharing, leading to inconsistencies in how data are collected, stored and shared.",
    "The lack of coordination and inconsistencies in data collection, management and analysis lead to a fragmented data landscape."
  ]
}